snippet.title: ✅  Amber Heard says reliving Johnny Depp break up has been 'incredibly painful'
snippet.description:
💖 Please Visit: https://www.facebook.com/Scathc/
💖 Please Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCQju4Bo1Tjk9SzhHQDknWaw?sub_confirmation=1
✍   spoke of her pain at having to relive her break up from Johnny Depp as she delivered a speech outside London's High Court.   Depp, 57, is suing News Group Newspapers (NGN) over a headline in The Sun labelling him a "wife beater" over egations he was physicy abusive to his then-wife Heard.  Depp says the claims are "sick and completely untrue".  The Pirates of the Caribbean star has said that he was never abusive to his ex-wife and has claimed that she was the abusive one in their relationship.  He's accused her of putting out a cigarette in his face and throwing a vodka bottle that severed his finger, among other things.   Heard, 34, denies his counter claims.  Speaking outside the High Court , she said: "I travelled here to the UK to testify as a witness to assist the court.  "After obtaining a restraining order in 2016 and finalising my divorce, I just wanted to move on with my life.  "I did not file this law suit and despite its significance, I would have preferred not to be here  ...
💖 #AmberHeard, #PiratesoftheCaribbean, #JohnnyDepp
